<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Aspiring Animators Hope Goldfish Will Help Them Land Jobs</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Christine Dellert
		
		<span class="date">May 5, 2009</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 345px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1754/en_US/atlasmain.jpg" height="226" width="345"  /> 
			
			<p>"Atlas' Revenge" is the work of about two dozen UCF students in the Digital Media department. The film's first screening will be Tuesday, May 5. </p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041046c64a5a0120ee76bff60078e2">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
					
						
						
						
					
			
			
			
		</div>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
